name: Transferencias pendientes de terminar
query:
select name,posting_date as Fecha,from_warehouse as Origen,tecnico,(case when per_transferred < 100 then 'Pendiente' else 'Listo' end) 'Transferido',
(case when docstatus=0 then 'Borrador' when docstatus=1 then 'Validado' when docstatus=2 then 'Cancelado' end )
 Estado  from `vw_Stock_Entry_al_Transito`
 where per_transferred < 100
